      <title>hexo搭建博客（1）</title>
      <link href="2021/04/24/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89/"/>
      <url>2021/04/24/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="第一步"><a href="#第一步" class="headerlink" title="第一步"></a>第一步</h2><p>下载安装nodejs</p><p>通过npm配置淘宝源 cnpm</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> -g cnpm --registry<span class="token operator">=</span>https://registry.npm.taobao.org</code></pre><p>查看cnpm版本</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">cnpm -v</code></pre><h2 id="第二步"><a href="#第二步" class="headerlink" title="第二步"></a>第二步</h2><p>通过cnpm下载安装hexo</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"> cnpm <span class="token function">install</span> -g hexo-cli</code></pre><p>hexo安装所在地址</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">D:\Nodejs\node_global\node_modules\hexo-cli\bin\hexo</code></pre><h2 id="第三步"><a href="#第三步" class="headerlink" title="第三步"></a>第三步</h2><p>创建一个自己博客所在的文件夹</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">D:\Myblog</code></pre><p>通过hexo初始化一个博客</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo init</code></pre><p>通过hexo server 命令启动服务，默认是在</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"> http://localhost:4000</code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
